{"pageProps":{"note":{"id":"g05lfgv5zmp5zwv7c40j8n1","title":"CSS snippets","desc":"","updated":1763622752132,"created":1646129148295,"custom":{},"fname":"dev.CSS.snippets","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"vault"},"contentHash":"f19b19df86165f4192a809114dcdee49","links":[],"anchors":{"collections":{"type":"header","text":"Collections","value":"collections","line":8,"column":0,"depth":2},"outlining-the-page":{"type":"header","text":"Outlining The Page","value":"outlining-the-page","line":13,"column":0,"depth":2},"image-inside-div-has-extra-space-below-the-image":{"type":"header","text":"Image inside div has extra space below the image","value":"image-inside-div-has-extra-space-below-the-image","line":28,"column":0,"depth":2},"how-to-align-the-text-of-the-last-paragraph-line":{"type":"header","text":"How to align the text of the last paragraph line","value":"how-to-align-the-text-of-the-last-paragraph-line","line":36,"column":0,"depth":2},"how-to-think-about-html-responsive-images":{"type":"header","text":"How to think about HTML responsive images","value":"how-to-think-about-html-responsive-images","line":40,"column":0,"depth":2},"the-power-of-has-in-css":{"type":"header","text":"The Power of :has() in CSS","value":"the-power-of-has-in-css","line":50,"column":0,"depth":2},"default-setting":{"type":"header","text":"Default setting","value":"default-setting","line":58,"column":0,"depth":2},"get-the-screen-width--height-without-javascript":{"type":"header","text":"Get The Screen Width & Height Without JavaScript","value":"get-the-screen-width--height-without-javascript","line":112,"column":0,"depth":2},"a-guide-to-image-overlays-in-css":{"type":"header","text":"A guide to image overlays in CSS","value":"a-guide-to-image-overlays-in-css","line":133,"column":0,"depth":2},"adactio":{"type":"header","text":"adactio","value":"adactio","line":161,"column":0,"depth":2},"the-universal-focus-ring":{"type":"header","text":"The Universal Focus Ring","value":"the-universal-focus-ring","line":196,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":["fhqiguqk4tmhvgqwol1sgku","47hsgmnzjkgzea5s5nrg8qx","db1iy80kfrgwmlb2ggnwf8p","utfpb5303hi2tjwtucpx4i9"],"parent":"14ndat1u737ts8fzosspizp","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"css-snippets\">CSS snippets<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#css-snippets\"></a></h1>\n<h2 id=\"collections\">Collections<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#collections\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://smolcss.dev\">SmolCSS</a>: Minimal snippets for modern CSS layouts and components</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://iamkate.com/code/tree-views/\">Tree views in css</a> - <code>details open</code></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"outlining-the-page\"><a href=\"https://ishadeed.com/article/threads-app-css-part-2/#outlining-the-page\">Outlining The Page</a><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#outlining-the-page\"></a></h2>\n<p>It‚Äôs important to remember that anything you see on the screen is a box, even if it‚Äôs a circle or a <code>1px</code> separator. Everything is a box.</p>\n<pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">*<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n*<span class=\"token pseudo-element\">:before</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n*<span class=\"token pseudo-element\">:after</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">outline</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> solid <span class=\"token number\">0.5</span><span class=\"token unit\">px</span> <span class=\"token hexcode color\">#db6a7d</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">border</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre>\n<p>An outline with <code>0.5px</code> width. I picked half a pixel so that it‚Äôs easier to look at the boxes. I also removed all borders as they cause confusion.</p>\n<h2 id=\"image-inside-div-has-extra-space-below-the-image\"><a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/questions/5804256/image-inside-div-has-extra-space-below-the-image\">Image inside div has extra space below the image</a><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#image-inside-div-has-extra-space-below-the-image\"></a></h2>\n<pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">img</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">display</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> block<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"how-to-align-the-text-of-the-last-paragraph-line\"><a href=\"https://www.stefanjudis.com/today-i-learned/how-to-align-the-text-of-the-last-paragraph-line/\">How to align the text of the last paragraph line</a><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#how-to-align-the-text-of-the-last-paragraph-line\"></a></h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p><code>text-align-last</code></p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"how-to-think-about-html-responsive-images\"><a href=\"https://danburzo.ro/responsive-images-html/\">How to think about HTML responsive images</a><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#how-to-think-about-html-responsive-images\"></a></h2>\n<pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#x3C;</span>picture</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#x3C;</span>source</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">media</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>(prefers-color-scheme: dark)<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">srcset</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>macos-dark.png<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#x3C;</span>source</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">media</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>print<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">srcset</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>macos-contrast.png<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#x3C;</span>img</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">src</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>macos-light.png<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">alt</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>‚Ä¶<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#x3C;/</span>picture</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n</code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"the-power-of-has-in-css\"><a href=\"https://css-tricks.com/the-power-of-has-in-css/\">The Power of :has() in CSS</a><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#the-power-of-has-in-css\"></a></h2>\n<pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">h1<span class=\"token pseudo-class\">:has</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token combinator\">+</span> h2<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token color\">blue</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"default-setting\">Default setting<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#default-setting\"></a></h2>\n<pre class=\"language-scss\"><code class=\"language-scss\"><span class=\"token comment\">// fonts</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">* </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  &#x26;<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">lang</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>ko<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">word-break</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> keep-all<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  &#x26;<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">lang</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>en<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">word-break</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> keep-all<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  &#x26;<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">lang</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>ja<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">word-break</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> normal<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">word-break</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> auto-phrase<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// From Chrome 119. https://developer.chrome.com/blog/css-i18n-features?hl=en</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">*,\ncode,\nkbd,\nsamp,\npre </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// Îî∞Î°ú ÏßÄÏ†ïÌïòÏßÄ ÏïäÍ≥† *Îßå Ïì∞Î©¥ ÎÇòÎ®∏ÏßÄ tagÎäî tailwind Í∏∞Î≥∏ reset styleÏù¥ Ï†ÅÏö©Îê®.</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">font-family</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Apple SD Gothic Neo\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> -apple-system<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> BlinkMacSystemFont<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Segoe UI\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    Roboto<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> Helvetica<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> Arial<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> sans-serif<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Apple Color Emoji\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Segoe UI Emoji\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token string\">\"Segoe UI Symbol\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">word-break</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> keep-all<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">-webkit-font-smoothing</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> antialiased<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// #region text-wrap - https://codersblock.com/blog/nicer-text-wrapping-with-css-text-wrap/#in-closing</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">h1,\nh2,\nh3,\nh4,\nh5,\nh6 </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">text-wrap</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> balance<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">div,\np </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">text-wrap</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> pretty<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// #endregion</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// reset</span>\n<span class=\"token atrule\"><span class=\"token rule\">@layer</span> reset</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token atrule\"><span class=\"token rule\">@tailwind</span> base<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n  body</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    @apply text-16 text-grey-900<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"get-the-screen-width--height-without-javascript\"><a href=\"https://css-tip.com/screen-dimension/\">Get The Screen Width &#x26; Height Without JavaScript</a><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#get-the-screen-width--height-without-javascript\"></a></h2>\n<pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token atrule\"><span class=\"token rule\">@property</span> <span class=\"token variable\">--_w</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">syntax</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"&#x3C;length>\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">inherits</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> true<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">initial-value</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">100</span><span class=\"token unit\">vw</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token atrule\"><span class=\"token rule\">@property</span> <span class=\"token variable\">--_h</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">syntax</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"&#x3C;length>\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">inherits</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> true<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">initial-value</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">100</span><span class=\"token unit\">vh</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\"><span class=\"token pseudo-class\">:root</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token variable\">--w</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token color\">tan</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token function\">atan2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token function\">var</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">--_w</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token unit\">px</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">/* screen width */</span>\n  <span class=\"token variable\">--h</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token color\">tan</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n    <span class=\"token function\">atan2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token function\">var</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">--_h</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token unit\">px</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">/* screen height*/</span> <span class=\"token comment\">/* The result is an integer without unit */</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"a-guide-to-image-overlays-in-css\"><a href=\"https://blog.logrocket.com/css-overlay/\">A guide to image overlays in CSS</a><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#a-guide-to-image-overlays-in-css\"></a></h2>\n<pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#x3C;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>image-wrapper<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#x3C;</span>img</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">src</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">alt</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>Sample Image<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">width</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>800<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">height</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>600<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#x3C;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>overlay-text<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>The Pros and Cons of Buying vs. Renting a Home<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#x3C;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#x3C;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n</code></pre>\n<pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\"><span class=\"token class\">.image-wrapper</span><span class=\"token pseudo-element\">::before</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">content</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">position</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> absolute<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">top</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">left</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">width</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">100</span><span class=\"token unit\">%</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">height</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">100</span><span class=\"token unit\">%</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">background</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token color\"><span class=\"token function\">rgba</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0.3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre>\n<pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\"><span class=\"token class\">.image-wrapper</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">position</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> relative<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">/* Other styles */</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"adactio\"><a href=\"https://adactio.com/journal/21896\">adactio</a><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#adactio\"></a></h2>\n<p>For instance, I‚Äôm a huge fan of view transitions and I enable them by default on every new project, but I do it like this:</p>\n<pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token atrule\"><span class=\"token rule\">@media</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token property\">prefers-reduced-motion</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> no-preference<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token atrule\"><span class=\"token rule\">@view-transition</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">navigation</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> auto<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre>\n<pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">ul<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\nol<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\ndl<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\ndt<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\ndd<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\np<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\nfigure<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\nblockquote</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">hanging-punctuation</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> first last<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">text-wrap</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> pretty<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">h1<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\nh2<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\nh3<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\nh4<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\nh5<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\nh6</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">text-align</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> center<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">text-wrap</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> balance<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"the-universal-focus-ring\"><a href=\"https://css-tip.com/universal-focus/\">The Universal Focus Ring</a><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#the-universal-focus-ring\"></a></h2>\n<pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">html<span class=\"token pseudo-element\">::after</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">content</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">position</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> fixed<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">position-anchor</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token variable\">--focus</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">inset</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">anchor</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>inside<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">outline</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token unit\">px</span> solid <span class=\"token color\">darkred</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">transition</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">0.4</span><span class=\"token uni